line_1: Amaz'd to see Her look so Prim,
line_2: And she admir'd as much at Him.

line_1: What Creature's that, so very pert and prim;
line_2: So very full of foppery, and whim;

line_1: SHE, who on earth was nice and prim,
Some whimsical trollop most like, says Miss Prim,
line_2: Has been scribbling of nonsense, just out of a whim,
